Description: Identifying hyphenation points in strings can be useful for both
    text processing and display functions. The 'Hunspell' hyphenation library
    provides tools to perform hyphenation using custom language rule dictionaries.
    Numerous hyphenation rules dictionaries are included. Words can be hyphenated
    directly or split into hyphenated component strings for further processing.
